snippet: After Duke overwhelmed North Carolina State on Saturday, 88-80, the Blue Devils may regain their ranking in the Associated Press Top 25 poll by Monday.
abstract: Marc Tracy On College Basketball column predicts Duke men's team will not be outside Associated Pres Top 25 poll for long; notes team has Division I’s most efficient offense and has improved to 17-6 over all and 6-4 in Atlantic Coast Conference with 88-80 win over North Carolina.
lead_paragraph: After Duke overwhelmed North Carolina State on Saturday, 88-80, the Blue Devils may regain their ranking in the Associated Press Top 25 poll by Monday.

headline.print_headline: Duke’s Absence From the Top 25 Is Likely to Be Brief
headline.main: Duke’s Absence From the Top 25 Is Likely to Be Brief
